      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_1300045963536821814.png",
                "id": "talent33085",
                "key": "Invoker's Spear",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Invoker's Spear"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span>'s Indwelling Level +1.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Gain 1 level of Indwelling. If Indwelling Level is at least 8, decrease the Indwelling level by 6.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Indwelling grants the following effects based on its level</span>:<br>If equal to or greater than 2: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>;<br>If equal to or greater than 4: DMG dealt +2.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/c5f5c789f46baf1c0c0ff52d5feabe9a_6779066959951187862.png",
                "id": "talent48308",
                "key": "Secret Rite: Chasmic Soulfarer",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Secret Rite: Chasmic Soulfarer"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span>'s Indwelling Level +2.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Gain 1 level of Indwelling. If Indwelling Level is at least 8, decrease the Indwelling level by 6.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Indwelling grants the following effects based on its level</span>:<br>If equal to or greater than 2: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>;<br>If equal to or greater than 4: DMG dealt +2.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/b6ab0891aede70ddf48bfa3859de14ea_8504213223073492021.png",
                "id": "talent60721",
                "key": "Sacred Rite: Wolf's Swiftness",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sacred Rite: Wolf's Swiftness"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Gain 1 level of Indwelling. If Indwelling Level is at least 8, decrease the Indwelling level by 6.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Indwelling grants the following effects based on its level</span>:<br>If equal to or greater than 2: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>;<br>If equal to or greater than 4: DMG dealt +2.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/8a173f8df2e58a9df74a6c3a74d385eb_7856491351343439898.png",
                "id": "talent3228",
                "key": "Lawful Enforcer",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lawful Enforcer"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/05/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_1940805754092367287.png",
                "id": "talent28663",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_783688252727416355.png",
